Whether you are heading off to college, moving in to a new house, or simply cleaning out your garage, Great Value Storage in Worthington, Ohio is here to help you with every step along the way. We are dedicated to providing you with the best in self storage. We offer climate-controlled units in a clean, secure environment. Our modern facility provides semester-long leases (perfect for students), month-to-month rentals, 24/7 access, and the friendliest staff in the Columbus and Ohio State University areas! 

You don’t have to live in Worthington to enjoy our services. Many of our tenants hail from communities like Polaris, Dublin-Granville, Dublin, and Columbus. You can purchase tenant insurance on our property and manage your monthly rent online.

We’ll be happy to tell you more about our moving dollies, delivery acceptance, perimeter fencing, ground-level rentals, wide driveways, and military discounts. You can also reach out to us with our online contact form.
